{"tid":1379650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online重要戰略]be water 的真正意義,衝衝仔/半衝衝仔/和理非請睇","createTime":"2019-07-28T23:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:07:02.000Z","uid":24123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3846a8c154881932cc4ab7284bf011fd223921e2","tid":1379650,"uid":24123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T23:02:14.000Z","msg":"呢個月keep 住online<br />\n發現好多人都以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>為 be water 係等如對方一打到黎散/退</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係覺得咁既人唔該開一盤水，然後一野打落盤水度睇下水會變成點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">水係會四方八面向施力方向彈過去</span></strong></span><br />\n如果對方一打你就退，sorry 你只係一舊磚<br />\n<br />\n以下係be water 實用篇:<br />\n<br />\n好似今晚咁，去到10點左其實我方人數仍然有好多人，但往往比30-40 (或更少) 既防暴就拖住左我地幾千人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時好似情況係咁(只憑記憶非準確):<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzjS2ic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwzjS2ic.png&h=c6b1420f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時大部分人都係上環到中環中間，德輔道中永樂街新紀元廣場文咸東街之間<br />\n<br />\n當啲怪一推進，大家都冇曬方向，向唔同方法走散..<br />\n<br />\n其實只要我方10倍於對方，對方就唔敢貿貿然推進，即係10個防暴怪只需大約100人就可以拖住佢地<br />\n<br />\nBe water should be 大家一齊走去班怪既其他方位<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>甚至後方去施加壓力</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n理想示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OExdMRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOExdMRt.png&h=421db543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點向班怪施壓？一衝上前佢地就放技，我好驚死喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家唔係叫你地衝上去同佢地打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water my friend <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係安全距離下遠攻或者叫囂已經有對對方壓力，幫到其他防線好多</span></strong></span><br />\n佢一放技你就走同救火，救完火再上返安全距離<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>講到呢度，亦都好想提下安全距離</strong></span><br />\n呢幾日係咁見到有班full gear既人企係前線，然後班防暴怪行前50米，自己就1212咁後退500米甚至更遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見住你地真心嬲，唔係要你地死守同佢地打，但出得黎可唔可以大膽啲？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你地實跑得快過班full gear 拎長盾既防暴怪架！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(唔計速龍)<br />\n<br />\n對住防暴怪基本上你只要留<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>150-200 米，佢實追唔到你</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n要守/玩，就留返呢個安全距離，咁樣先可以掩護到其他人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">另外真心唔明白點解到今時今日仲有人叫唔好扔野</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遠攻係我地唯一既有效還擊手段(詳細情況去睇返幾年前旺角既片啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，近戰真心係裝備同心態上同對方未係對等<br />\n<br />\n如果要頂住對方推進，一定要遠攻/魔攻，set 防線係冇撚用架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發現大家有鋪癮，就係好鐘意set 所謂既防線</span></strong></span><br />\n大家唔知係咪玩得AOE 太多，以為set 起左個防線就會自動攻擊啲怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n防線係阻住佢前進，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>佢地要過防線就要拆/跨過去，呢個就係我地要發動攻勢既時機</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSet 完防線又唔守，set 黎有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係set 又唔守，幾分鐘就俾人折曬啦，有咩大作用呢？<br />\n<br />\n我知道面對住full gear 既怪一定會有恐懼，但你地都已經on左line 啦，懇請大家拎出你哋嘅勇氣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>行前多兩步/走慢兩步，對戰局會有決定性嘅影響</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n亦都經常有人叫&rdquo;走啦，留係呢度冇作用啦/留返條命第日再出過黎&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我哋一日喺仲留條街度，就對呢個政府構成多1秒嘅壓力<br />\n我哋出嚟就係為咗比呢個政府壓力！直到佢哋聆聽我哋嘅訴求！爭取到我地要既野！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家記住，我地而家係搞革命</span></span></strong></span>！唔係簡單既示威<br />\n<br />\n革命會流血會受傷，但係要爭取到自由，為咗我哋嘅屋企，呢個係必經階段！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"031af5472eda3d0fc3cfdeb0d410aea79c889d42","tid":1379650,"uid":24123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:22:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f06cce66f80caa653e5a6290aa31ef42b98693ec","tid":1379650,"uid":185513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:40:55.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca7fcdb11811395f33c43591dfea17b101bf215","tid":1379650,"uid":24123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff35dd77caf0305fe56b23b36a08ce7637a33a6","tid":1379650,"uid":24123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4d6cb38837864fa80513ae01c057b0e4af51e9","tid":1379650,"uid":24123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3717f11d8958088973bee58af94b33126029750","tid":1379650,"uid":24123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"係咪長文冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251df025a8d2c6dd450d61929d85b788cb8c33aa","tid":1379650,"uid":24123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:21:24.000Z",